         heh..if you don't like being under 50percent health while solo'ing, pick another class ;)</P><P>Seriously though, I wouldn't worry about it.  It's not like you can't get your health back easily.</P><P>You will ping pong your health and mana bar a lot with the lich line.  Just something to have to get used to.</P><P>**EDIT**</P><P>I would get a partner, and go kill hill giants.  Save up 400pp, which shouldn't take you long, and go buy 2 5ac 55hp rings.  They go for around 200pp each on my server, whereas the 6ac 65hp rings go for 550pp each.  IMO, it's not worth 350pp for the 1ac 10hp difference.</P><P>Good luck!</P><P>Nephylum<BR><font color=purple>"No rest for the wicked"</font id=purple><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=265499" target="_blank">My stuff</a></P><P>Edited by - Nephylum on 06/27/2002  14:09:23<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
