         I've just been upgrading my equipment these last few levels, going for hp gear mainly, and so far I have 839hp's and 1217mana at 37th level.  I've still got to upgrade 5 slots of equipment that are still cloth, or as good as.  Here's a few nice little items:</P><P><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=776" target="_blank">Bracelet of Woven Grass</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7475" target="_blank">Fungus Crown</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1301" target="_blank">Gatorscale Leggings</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2237" target="_blank">Gatorscale Sleeves</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2179" target="_blank">Cloak of the Ice Bear</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1767" target="_blank">Shadowbound Boots</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1919" target="_blank">Black Sapphire Electrum Earring</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=4243" target="_blank">Velium Fire Wedding Ring</a><BR><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1020" target="_blank">Embroidered Black Cape</a></P><P>All that is pretty doable at your level.  For stuff you can't or don't want to camp, fight the Druids in WC, you get tonnes of cash from them and you can solo them too at your level.  They are what I used to get the cash for my jewellery.</P><P>Rakis (<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=215309" target="_blank">Magelo</a>)<BR>37th level Necro<BR>UK resident of <a href="http://pub96.ezboard.com/bkanebaylecommunitycenter" target="_blank">Kane Bayle</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
