        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The reason why its taking so much more hp is mainly due to the fact that your mana pool grows as you level.  So what used to take a minute with Allure on would take you a bit more now.  As lich upgrades into demi lich and arch lich the ratio gets a bit better and faster.  You loose hp fast if you arent careful.</P><P>Darque Evilfro 58th <BR>Begger of the 200th Copper <BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=226497" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=226497</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
